question:
Consider the following recursive function that computes the sum of elements in an array:

function sumArray(arr, n) {
    if (n == 0) {
        return 0;
    }
    return arr[n-1] + sumArray(arr, n-1);
}

Trace the execution of sumArray([3, 7, 2, 5], 4) step by step. What is the final return value?
